They are attracted to the prospect of manipulation of virtual objects in the air with bare hands and the creation of virtual open spaces.
- Please, in general terms, what is the subject of study of your research group?
We engage in person-computer interaction, but we also try to broaden the limits of this interaction.
For now humanity in its large mass has been trapped in the stage of working with the pixels of the flat screen, sometimes touching it with the finger.
